Package: visualizer
Title: Visual Add-on Facilitating the Creation of Charts with ggplot2
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Alba", "Maiques", , "maiques@hotmail.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: VisualizeR is an R package offering an intuitive graphical interface 
    that makes it simple and efficient to create and customize plots using ggplot2. 
    Through a layer-based system, it allows users to visually configure each element 
    of a ggplot2 plot, reducing the complexity of the syntax while retaining the 
    full flexibility of the ggplot2 graphics engine. This package is designed for 
    users of all levels, from beginners looking to explore plot creation to advanced 
    users aiming to streamline their visualization process.
